Definition: causing loss of physical or intellectual bearings
Example: making so many turns to the right and then the left was completely disorienting; a sharp blow to the head can be disorienting
Synonyms: ORIENTING, UNORIENTED, causing, loss, of, physical, or, intellectual, bearings, making, so, many, turns, to, the, right, and, then, left, was, completely, disorienting, a, sharp, blow, head, can, be
Category: adj.all
